snippet.textDisplay: I didn't feel the energy from Momotaz. The music team has failed to utilize her talent. She is such a natural singer. You guys should let her sing the way she always does. That will work. On the other hand, Mizan and the chorus team did well. However, after the first hit song, NASEK NASEK expectations went high. This song was not able to keep the balance. I would like to believe the next one will be different and will touch everybody's heart. Best wishes.
snippet.textOriginal: I didn't feel the energy from Momotaz. The music team has failed to utilize her talent. She is such a natural singer. You guys should let her sing the way she always does. That will work. On the other hand, Mizan and the chorus team did well. However, after the first hit song, NASEK NASEK expectations went high. This song was not able to keep the balance. I would like to believe the next one will be different and will touch everybody's heart. Best wishes.
